T02TD2104E:134a-1: ti la ka ae ka n'a ma /
T02TD2104E:134a-3: thig le gcig pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2104E:134a-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2104E:134a-5: rang bzhin bde ba brnyes pa yi //
T02TD2104E:134a-6: ye shes sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2104E:134a-7: dmigs pa la ni sems bzhag nas //
T02TD2104E:134a-8: sbyor pa ye shes thig le bshad //
T02TD2104E:134a-9: sna tshogs chos kun shes rab kyis bltas nas //
T02TD2104E:134a-10: gcig dang du ma mtha' yis brtags pa dang //
T02TD2104E:134a-11: gcig kyang mi dmigs rang bzhin stong pa yin //
T02TD2104E:134a-12: thams cad rig pa'i ngo bor gsal 'gyur pa //
T02TD2104E:134a-13: gnyis kyi mtha' yis dben pa gnyis med de //
T02TD2104E:134a-14: rnam pa thams cad ldan pa ye shes skur //
T02TD2104E:134a-15: bsgoms te sa bon nyid du sems gnas bya //
T02TD2104E:134a-16: de la dmigs pa nye ba nyid du gyur pa ni //
T02TD2104E:134a-17: gsal dang mi gsal phyi ma'i blo yis brtags na yid kyi yi ge nyid //
T02TD2104E:134a-18: rjes la 'gro ba rnam par dag byas la //
T02TD2104E:134a-19: rten dang brten pa skul ba'i ku ru bzhag / yi ge la sems gzung ba'i thig le dang po'o /
T02TD2104E:134a-21: // / thabs dang shes rab kha sbyor la //
T02TD2104E:134a-22: shigs pa med pa'i yi ge nas //
T02TD2104E:134a-23: tshangs pa'i mig gsum bzhi yis bskor //
T02TD2104E:134a-24: de la rnam shes brtan pa dang //
T02TD2104E:134a-25: 'dren pa brgyad dang dgur ldan pa'o //
T02TD2104E:134a-26: bde ba'i lhag pa'i bzlas pa bya //
T02TD2104E:134a-27: reg bya chen po skyes pa ni //
T02TD2104E:134a-28: lhag pa'i thig le chen por bsdu //
T02TD2104E:134a-29: mthar phyin reg bya skyes pa na //
T02TD2104E:134a-30: steng gi gnas su 'pho bar bya //
T02TD2104E:134a-31: reg bya la sems gzung ba'i thig le ste gnyis pa'o /
T02TD2104E:134a-33: // / ye shes sems dpa' rab mdzes sku //
T02TD2104E:134a-34: zla ba ltar rgyas rdo rje la //
T02TD2104E:134a-35: bcu drug thig le gcig pa gang //
T02TD2104E:134b-0: bcu @134b bdun ldan par bzlas bya ste //
T02TD2104E:134b-2: 'jug pa thig la bzlas pa bya //
T02TD2104E:134b-3: gsal dang bde dang yongs rdzogs nas //
T02TD2104E:134b-4: dbyu gu drug cu'i grangs su bgrang //
T02TD2104E:134b-6: bag dang ldan pa'i sbyor bas brtsam //
T02TD2104E:134b-7: phra mo la sems gzung ba'i thig le stee gsum pa'o /
T02TD2104E:134b-9: // / rnam par shes pa'i rdo rje'i sku /
T02TD2104E:134b-10: gangg'a'i klung gi sangs rgyas kyis //
T02TD2104E:134b-11: byin gyis brlabs la bsgom par bya //
T02TD2104E:134b-12: de nyid ye shes thig le bsgom //
T02TD2104E:134b-13: mi shigs sa bon 'dzin pa can //
T02TD2104E:134b-14: dran pa lhan cig skyes pa gsal //
T02TD2104E:134b-16: yul min shes pa'i mtshan nyid ni ;
T02TD2104E:134b-17: / gnas pa'i thig le rdzogs pa yi //
T02TD2104E:134b-18: cung zad mi gsal phra mor gsang //
T02TD2104E:134b-19: ye shes la sems gsang ba'i thig le ste bzhi pa'o /
T02TD2104E:134b-21: // / rnal 'byor lam la bslab pa ni //
T02TD2104E:134b-22: steng dang 'og gi mdud pa la //
T02TD2104E:134b-23: aom dang h'um gi thig le blta //
T02TD2104E:134b-24: thig le stong pa'i sa bon las //
T02TD2104E:134b-25: a'a li k'a li 'dzag pa'i phreng //
T02TD2104E:134b-26: rlung gis mnan la so kar bstim //
T02TD2104E:134b-27: de la legs rol skyes pa dang //
T02TD2104E:134b-28: 'og gi thig le stong pa las //
T02TD2104E:134b-29: nyis 'gyur phul la steng du bstim //
T02TD2104E:134b-30: de la legs rol skyes bas na //
T02TD2104E:134b-31: rang 'byung ye shes chen po bsgom //
T02TD2104E:134b-32: dbang po lnga la yi ges khyab //
T02TD2104E:134b-33: yul lnga legs rol chen por bsgom //
T02TD2104E:134b-34: de nas bcom ldan 'das ma las //
T02TD2104E:134b-35: thig le yi ge med pa gnyis //
T02TD2104E:134b-36: dbugs 'byung chen po bdag med bsgom //
T02TD2104E:134b-37: lhan cig skyes dga' rna ba'i dus //
T02TD2104E:134b-38: gsal stong bde ba dbyer med pa //
T02TD2104E:134b-39: gnyug ma nyams su myong bas shes //
T02TD2104E:134b-40: gal te mi gsal gyur pa na //
T02TD2104E:134b-41: rdo rje'i bzlas pa brtsam par bya //
T02TD2104E:134b-42: sbyor ba las byung 'od gsal sems //
T02TD2104E:134b-43: rnam par shes pa'i chos nyid 'das //
T02TD2104E:134b-44: ye shes gnyis med tshul 'chang ba //
T02TD2104E:134b-45: rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2104E:134b-46: dus gsum sangs rgyas las byed pa //
T02TD2104E:134b-47: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
T02TD2104E:134b-48: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa ;
T02TD2104E:134b-49: / ye shes mig gcig dri ma med //
T02TD2104E:134b-50: ye shes lus can de bzhin gshegs //
T02TD2104E:134b-51: thig le chen po grub pa bstan pa ste lnga pa'o /
T02TD2104E:134b-53: // / man ngag bdud rtsi lta bu grol ba'i rim pa thig la grub pa gsal byed gcig pa bstan /
T02TD2104E:134b-54: 'di las byung ba'i bsod nams ji snyed des //
T02TD2104E:135a-1: gnas dngos rnyed par shog / thig le gcig pa zhes bya ba //
T02TD2104E:135a-2: slob dpon dpal ldan gnyis su med pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2104E:135a-4: // / rnal 'byor ba bsod snyoms pa pra dzhy'a shr'i dzny'a na k'irtis rang 'gyur du mdzad pa'o//
